graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Controller"
        Controller["modelmesh-controller<br/>(Go Operator / controller-runtime)"]
        Webhook["ServingRuntime Webhook<br/>(Validating Webhook / 9443)"]
        EventStream["ModelMesh Event Stream<br/>(etcd Watcher)"]
        GRPCResolver["gRPC Resolver<br/>(kube:// Kubernetes Service Discovery)"]

        Controller -->|validates via| Webhook
        EventStream -->|dispatches GenericEvent| Controller
        GRPCResolver -->|discovers endpoints| Controller
    end

    subgraph "ModelMesh Pod (per ServingRuntime)"
        direction TB
        MM["ModelMesh Container<br/>(Data Plane / 8033 gRPC)"]
        Runtime["Runtime Container<br/>(Triton / MLServer / OVMS / TorchServe)"]
        Puller["Puller Sidecar<br/>(Model Storage Helper / 8086 gRPC)"]
        RESTProxy["REST Proxy Sidecar<br/>(HTTP→gRPC / 8008)"]
        OAuthProxy["OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>(HTTPS / 8443)"]

        OAuthProxy -->|HTTP/8008| RESTProxy
        RESTProxy -->|gRPC/8033| MM
        MM -->|gRPC/localhost| Runtime
        Puller -->|gRPC/8085| Runtime
    end

    User["Data Scientist / Client"] -->|gRPC/8033<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS| MM
    User -->|HTTPS/8443<br/>OAuth Token| OAuthProxy

    %% CRDs
    PredictorCR["Predictor CR<br/>(serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1)"]
    InferenceServiceCR["InferenceService CR<br/>(serving.kserve.io/v1beta1)"]
    ServingRuntimeCR["ServingRuntime CR<br/>(serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1)"]
    ClusterServingRuntimeCR["ClusterServingRuntime CR<br/>(serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1)"]

    User -->|creates| PredictorCR
    User -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR
    User -->|creates| ServingRuntimeCR

    PredictorCR -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceServiceCR -->|bridged to Predictor| Controller
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ClusterServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller

    %% Controller actions
    Controller -->|creates/updates| Deployment["Deployment<br/>(template-based construction)"]
    Controller -->|creates/updates| Service["Headless Service<br/>(modelmesh-serving)"]
    Controller -->|creates/updates| HPA["HorizontalPodAutoscaler"]
    Controller -->|gRPC commands| MM

    Deployment -->|manages| MM

    %% External dependencies
    Controller -->|state store| etcd["etcd<br/>(2379/TCP)"]
    EventStream -->|watches keys| etcd
    MM -->|model registry| etcd
    Puller -->|downloads models| Storage["External Storage<br/>(S3 / GCS / Azure / PVC)"]
    Controller -->|API calls| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API<br/>(443/TCP)"]

    %% Styling
    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style EventStream fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style GRPCResolver fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style MM fill:#50c878,color:#fff
    style Runtime fill:#50c878,color:#fff
    style Puller fill:#50c878,color:#fff
    style RESTProxy fill:#50c878,color:#fff
    style OAuthProxy fill:#50c878,color:#fff
    style PredictorCR fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style InferenceServiceCR fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style ServingRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style ClusterServingRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style etcd fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Storage fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
